360
00:21:48.952 --> 00:21:52.792
There are some promising treatment like lactoferrin supplementation

361
00:21:52.852 --> 00:21:56.372
to reduce metal mouth or liposomal spray to reduce

362
00:21:56.392 --> 00:21:59.432
