537
00:32:09.924 --> 00:32:13.304
And these have intermediate prevalence and intermediate lifespan.

538
00:32:14.044 --> 00:32:17.884
And then the third, type three cells are known to be

539
00:32:17.944 --> 00:32:21.924
sour sensors and may be high salt detectors

540
00:32:22.044 --> 00:32:23.624
in the circumvallate papillae.

541
00:32:24.884 --> 00:32:27.864
Now, all of these cells are renewed

542
00:32:28.284 --> 00:32:32.164
rapidly, really every two months, they're all new, from

543
00:32:32.174 --> 00:32:35.144
