00:34:37.265 --> 00:34:40.685
in human, but there's a single one in mice.

578
00:34:41.484 --> 00:34:45.104
And they're innervated by the same sets of cranial nerves that innervate those same

579
00:34:45.144 --> 00:34:46.424
types of buds in human.

