01:24:26.818 --> 01:24:30.688
us. And definitely needing to close those know-do gaps in time when we've got

1444
01:24:30.698 --> 01:24:33.178
more evidence through the development of clinical guidelines.

1445
01:24:34.218 --> 01:24:37.658
We want to stay in touch with you. I think I've said that, and maybe as we finish

